25
00:01:00,519 --> 00:01:02,519
Conquistar o mundo junto com você.

26
00:01:02,519 --> 00:01:03,519
É!

27
00:01:03,519 --> 00:01:04,519
É.

28
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,519
É crocante.

29
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:06,519
Sim.

